
VARIOUS IDEAS:
==============

- Support for ripping from BIN/CUE files.
- ID3 Tagging.
- Ogg/Vorbis Support.
- Progress bar in window title.
- Multithreading support.
- Realtime output naming and ID3 tagging.
- Localisation support.
- Recursive option.

Samplein.c
==========
- Support for resampling.
- Support for more WAV/AIFF subtypes.
- Read ahead buffer support.
- Support for ripping from BIN/CUE files.

DLL
===
- New complementary C-style interface.



